N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 8 ยง 564.6 - Towing

State Regulations

The college reserves the authority to remove by towing, at the owner's expense, any motor vehicle which is not registered or which is
parked in violation of campus parking regulations. Notes
